## Optimization Summary - Q7 Iteration 10

### Bottleneck Analysis (from Iter 8 baseline)
- **Load: 568.56 ms (46% of total)** ← PRIMARY BOTTLENECK
- Build: 610.31 ms (50% of total) ← SECONDARY BOTTLENECK
- Join & Aggregate: 42.77 ms (3% of total) - already fast
